EXPRESSION: CASE WHEN coalesce(trim(lastupdatedate),'') = '' THEN timestamp'1000-01-03 00:00:00.000GMT+7' ELSE CAST(substring(trim(lastupdatedate),1,4)||'-'||substring(trim(lastupdatedate),6,2)||'-'||substring(trim(lastupdatedate),9,2)||' '||substring(trim(lastupdatedate),12,2)||':'||substring(trim(lastupdatedate),15,2)||':'||substring(trim(lastupdatedate),18,2)AS TIMESTAMP)+ INTERVAL '7' HOUR END
